        <hr />
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between flex-wrap gap-2 small" style="color:var(--text-muted)">
            <span>&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year TechSpecs. All rights reserved.</span>
            <span><i class="bi bi-shield-check me-1" style="color:var(--primary)"></i>ASP.NET Core MVC 8 · PostgreSQL · AI Builder</span>
        </div>
